    <p>Most shoulder programs are designed for athletes or clinical settings. They include eight to twelve exercises, resistance bands in four colors, and progressions that require 45 minutes and a gym membership.</p>
    <p>The result? People start, get overwhelmed, fall off, and conclude that "nothing works for my shoulders." The truth is: the program didn't match the goal.</p>
    <h3 style="margin-top:28px;">Introducing the TC Fitness Shoulder Reset System</h3>
    <p>Four exercises. Selected for one reason: the greatest return on investment for adults dealing with shoulder tightness, postural imbalance, and pain with overhead activities.</p>
